                                                                              rdfs:label "RIVM" .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#Radiation
<http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#Radiation> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                                   rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#RiskType> ;
